 |        |                          hi      |        |      |      |
 |        |                           !      |        |
 |        |                           !      |        |
 |        |&lt;============ wid =========+=====&gt;|        |
 |        |                           !      |        |
 |        |                           !      |        |
 |        |                           !      |        |
 |        |                           v      |        |
 |        ------------------------------------        |
 |                           ^                        |
 |                          vbs                       |
 |                                                    |
 ------------------------------------------------------
                             ^
                            vss
                        - ------- -
                             ^
                            vse
                        - ------- -
                             ^
                            vbe
</pre>
